'''Energy in Portugal''' describes [[World energy resources and consumption|energy]] and [[Electricity generation|electricity]] production, consumption and import in [[Portugal]]. [[Energy policy of Portugal]] will describe the [[politics of Portugal]] related to energy more in detail. [[Electricity sector in Portugal]] is the main article of electricity in Portugal.
